\mt1 Šł§aggay  
\c 1
\s1 Acejje…õ i u…õawed n Ňôebni n Zzawect Tameqqrant  
\m
\v 1 Deg usegg ∑as wiss tnayen n uje«ßid Dariyus, deg uyur wiss setta, deg wass amezwaru n uyur, yusa-dd wawaŇô n SIDI, s ufus n Šł§aggay, anabi, …£ar Zarubbabil, mmis n Ca‚Äôaltiyal, lwali n Yahuda, u …£ar Yahuca…õ mmis n YahuŠĻ£adaq, arrays n ikehhanen, inna:  
\v 2 ‚ÄúAmmu i issawaŇô SIDI n Ňô…õeskar, iqqar: Ňėgens-a iqqar: ‚Äė∆źad war dd-yiwiŠłć ŇôŠł•aŇô, ŇôŠł•aŇô maŠł•end ad tŠĶČttwabna Taddart n SIDI …õawed.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
