\v 3 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd wawaŇô n SIDI s ufus n unabi Šł§aggay, inna:  
\v 4 ‚ÄúMa yiwed-dd ŇôŠł•aŇô Šł•ima kenniw ad tzed…£em di tudrin nwem ittwaseqqfen, \add am\add* Taddart-a d Ňôxarbet?  
\v 5 \add Maca\add* Ňôexxu inna SIDI n Ňô…õeskarat: Šł§Šłćam mliŠł• ibriden nwem \add deg\add* wuŇôawen nwem ...  
\v 6 Kenniw tzarr…õem aŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠as, tmejjarem drus. Kenniw tŠĶČttettem, war tŠĶČttjjiwinem, kenniw tsessem, \add maca\add* war i«ßi aŇôami i …£a tescarem, kenniw tyarŠłćem arruŠłć, \add maca\add* war issŠł•emmi, u wenni d …£a iŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠fen Ňômunet, ad iŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠ef Ňômunet deg ict n tkemmust tŠĶČnnuqqeb. \x ‚óė \xo 1:6 \xt A…õwd. 28:38; Mixa 6:14, 15\x*  
\v 7 Ammu i iqqar SIDI n Ňô…õeskar: Šł§Šłćam mliŠł• ibriden nwem \add deg\add* wuŇôawen nwem.  
\v 8 Ge…õ…õdem adrar, awyem-dd akeccuŠłć u bnam Taddart-a u Necc ad xas arŠłći…£ u ad zzayes ttwass…õu«ße…£, inna SIDI.  
\v 9 Kenniw tarrim taynit i waŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠as \add n Ňô…£i«ßet\add*, \add maca\add* xzarem, \add aqa-t\add* m…£ir drus u xmi t-i-dd-tŠĶČttawyem …£ar taddart, Necc ttsuŠłće…£ xas. Mayemmi? \add Ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI n Ňô…õeskarat. Zi ssibbet n Taddart inu tenni \add idewŇôen\add* d Ňôxarbet, \add am\add* kuŇô ijjen \add zzaywem\add* ittazzeŇô x taddart \add n yixef\add* nnes.  
\v 10 X uya menn…õen xawem ijenwan nnda u tammurt tmenne…õ \add xawem\add* Ňô…£i«ßet nnes. \x ‚óė \xo 1:10 \xt A…õwd. 28:23\x*  
\v 11 Necc Ňôa…£i…£-dd x ŇôekŠł•eŠłć i temmurt, x idurar, x imendi, x binu, x zzect, u x marra min i dd-tŠĶČttawi temmurt, uŇôa x iwdan u x ŇômaŇô u x warber n ifassen.‚ÄĚ   
\m
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* isŇôa Zarubbabil, mmis n Ca‚Äôaltiyal, u \add akides\add* Yahuca…õ, mmis n YahuŠĻ£adaq, arrays n ikehhanen, u marra min iqqimen n Ňôgens, …£ar tmijja n SIDI, AREBBI nsen, u …£ar wawaŇôen n unabi Šł§aggay, am mammec i t issekk SIDI, AREBBI nsen. U nitni, Ňôgens, gg ∑eden zzat i wudem n SIDI.  
\v 13 IbarreŠł• Šł§aggay, amsexxar n SIDI, i Ňôgens, inna: ‚ÄúNecc aqa ayi akidwem!‚ÄĚ iqqar SIDI.  
\v 14 Uca issekkar SIDI buŠł•beŇô n Zarubbabil, mmis n Ca‚Äôaltiyal, lwali n Yahuda, uŇôa d buŠł•beŇô n Yahuca…õ, mmis n YahuŠĻ£adaq, arrays n ikehhanen, uŇôa d buŠł•beŇô n marra min iqqimen zi Ňôgens u nitni usin-dd u ggin Ňôxedmet di Taddart n SIDI n Ňô…õeskarat, AREBBI nsen.  
\v 15 deg wass wiss areb…õa u-…õicrin n uyur, deg uyur wiss setta, deg usegg ∑as wiss tnayen n uje«ßid Dariyus.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 2
\s1 A…õu«ßi n Zzawect Tameqqrant n jdid  
\m
\v 1 Deg uyur wiss seb…õa, deg wass wiss waŠł•it u-…õicrin n uyur, yusa-dd wawaŇô n SIDI s ufus n Šł§aggay, inna:  
\v 2 ‚ÄúSiweŇô xenni …£ar Zarubbabil, mmis n Ca…õaltiyil, lwali n Yahuda, u …£ar Yahuca…õ, mmis n YahuŠĻ£adaq, arrays n ikehhanen, u …£ar min iqqimen zi Ňôgens, ini:  
\v 3 Wi zzaywem iqqimen zeg inni iŠļďrin \add …õad\add* Taddart-a s u…õu«ßi nnes amezwaru? D mammec i tt tŠĶČttwaŇôam Ňôexxu? Ma war te«ßi jar tiŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠awin nwem am walu?  
\v 4 Maca Ňôexxu, mŠł•eŠłć, \add a\add* Zarubbabil, iqqar SIDI, mŠł•eŠłć, \add a\add* Yahuca…õ, mmis n YahuŠĻ£adaq, arrays n ikehhanen, meŠł•Šłćem \add kenniw\add* marra imezda…£ n temmurt, iqqar SIDI. Kkarem …£ar Ňôxedmet, ma…£ar Necc aqa ayi akidwem, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI n Ňô…õeskarat.  
\v 5 AwaŇô i zi ggi…£ ijj n Ňė…õahd akidwem, Ňôami dd-teff…£em zi MiŠĻ£ra, u ArruŠł• inu, aqa aten \add s tnayen idsen\add* bedden di ŇôwesŠĻ≠ nwem. War ttegg ∑edem ca!  
\v 6 Ma…£ar ammu i iqqar SIDI n Ňô…õeskarat: ∆źad ict n twaŇôa, \add m…£ir\add* drus n ŇôŠł•aŇô, Necc ad ssenhezze…£ ijenwan d temmurt, ŇôebŠł•ar d Ňôbarr. \x ‚óė \xo 2:6 \xt ∆źbr. 12:26, 27\x*   
\m
\v 7 Necc ad jje…£ marra Ňôegnus ad arjijen u ad dd-asen \add s\add* min i…£Ňôan aŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠as zi marra Ňôegnus u Necc ad ccure…£ Taddart-a \add s\add* u…õu«ßi!, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI n Ňô…õeskarat.  
\v 8 Inu nnuqart u inu wure…£, iqqar SIDI n Ňô…õeskarat.  
\v 9 A…õu«ßi n Taddart-a taneggarut ad yiŇôi d ameqqran x wenni n \add Taddart\add* tamezwarut, iqqar SIDI n Ňô…õeskarat, u Necc ad wce…£ Ňôehna deg wemcan-a, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI n Ňô…õeskarat.‚ÄĚ   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Ijj n Ňôgens ixmej ad iŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠ef lbaraka  
\m
\v 10 Deg wass wiss areb…õa u-…õicrin n uyur wiss tes…õa, deg usegg ∑as wiss tnayen n Dariyus, yusa-dd wawaŇô n SIDI s ufus n Šł§aggay, inna:  
\v 11 ‚ÄúAmmu i iqqar SIDI n Ňô…õeskarat: Seqsam xenni ikehhanen \add x\add* Ccari…õa, ini:  
\v 12 Xzar, ijjen iksi aysum iqeddsen deg ubeŠł•rur n warruŠłć nnes u s ubeŠł•rur nnes iŠł•ada a…£rum ni…£ min iwennan ni…£ binu ni…£ zzect ni…£ min ma ittemwaccan, ma man aya ad idweŇô iqeddes?‚ÄĚ Uca arrin-dd ikehhanen, nnan ‚ÄúLla!‚ÄĚ  
\v 13 Uca inna Šł§aggay: ‚ÄúMaŇôa ijj idweŇô ixmej zeg ict n Ňôxecbet, uca xenni iŠł•ada ca zi marra man aya, ma man aya ad idweŇô \add xenni\add* ixmej?‚ÄĚ Arrin-dd \add xas\add* ikehhanen, nnan: ‚ÄúAd idweŇô ixmej!‚ÄĚ \x ‚óė \xo 2:13 \xt ŇėxŇô. 5:2; 9:6-7, 10\x*  
\v 14 \add Ňėexdenni\add* yarra-dd Šł§aggay, inna: ‚ÄúAmmu i ye«ßa Ňôgens-a u ammu i ye«ßa Ňôgens-a zzat i wudem inu, iqqar SIDI, u ammu i te«ßa marra Ňôxedmet n ifassen nsen u min qeddmen d ddbiŠł•et, aqa-tt ixmej.  
\v 15 \add Maca\add* Ňôexxu, zeg wass-a d tsawent ggem uŇôawen nwem \add x man aya\add*: QbeŇô ma ittwassars weŠļďŇôu x weŠļďru di Zzawect Tameqqrant n SIDI,  
\v 16 qbeŇô ma ad imsar uya, yusa-dd yijjen …£ar yijj n u…õurric n imendi n …õicrin n Ňôeqyas, ammu i tu…£a \add din\add* m…£ir …õecra, \add u\add* yusa-dd yijj …£ar yict n tsirt \add n uŠłćiŇô\add*, Šł•ima ad yayem xemsin n ibarmiŇôen, ammu tu…£a \add din\add* m…£ir …õicrin.  
\v 17 Necc wti…£ kenniw s \add imendi\add* ittwasscemŠłćen \add zeg usemmiŠłć\add*, s jjriŠł•ect n wefsu u s tebrurri, \add wti…£\add* marra Ňôxedmet n ifassen nwem, \add maca\add* kenniw war dd …£ari tedwiŇôem ca, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. \x ‚óė \xo 2:17 \xt Šł§ag. 1:11\x*   
\m
\v 18 Zeg wass-a d tsawent ggem uŇôawen nwem x man aya, zeg wass wiss areb…õa u-…õicrin n uyur wiss tes…õa, zeg wass nni di ittwassars dsas n Zzawect Tameqqrant n SIDI, ggem uŇôawen nwem \add x man aya\add*,  
\v 19 ma aqa din zzarri…õet di tesraft? Tazayart d wartu n tazart d tcejjart n aremman d tcejjart n zzitun war dd-iwyen \add …õad\add* Ňô…£i«ßet! Zeg wass-a Necc ad barke…£!‚ÄĚ   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Lwa…õd i Zarubbabil  
\m
\v 20 Deg wass wiss areb…õa u-…õicrin yusa-dd wawaŇô n SIDI i Šł§aggay i twaŇôa wiss tnayen, inna:  
\v 21 ‚ÄúSiweŇô …£ar Zarubbabil, lwali n Yahuda, ini: Necc ad ssennhezze…£ ijenwan d temmurt,  
\v 22 u Necc ad ssenqeŇôbe…£ Ňô…õarc n tgeldin d tzemmar n tgeldin n¬†Ňôegnus, Necc ad ssenqeŇôbe…£ ikarruten \add n umen…£i\add* s yinni i ten ineddhen uŇôa d yiysan ak-d imnayen nsen ad ttwa…£eŠłćŇôen, kuŇô ijj di ssif n wenne…£ni. \f ‚óľ \fr 2:22 \ft \+fk n wenne…£ni\ft  - s T…õibranit ‚Äės umas‚Äô.\f*  
\v 23 \bd Deg wass nni\bd*, iqqar SIDI n Ňô…õeskarat, Necc ad cek ksi…£, Zarubbabil, mmis n Ca‚Äôaltiyal, amsexxar inu, iqqar SIDI, u Necc ad cek arre…£ d txadent n ucemme…õ, ma…£ar Necc ixŠłćare…£ cek!, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI n Ňô…õeskarat.‚ÄĚ   